  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Iron Onslaught is a wave-based game where you survive an endless wave of bots and mechs, and the only way to survive is to kill to unlock new weapons before you're overpowered by them. So sit back, relax, and survive the ever-growing horde.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Kill To Get New Weapons</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3569050/extras/2c3f7479a496a98d1d7336e20602ed93.poster.avif?t=1769385390\" width=600 height=600 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3569050/extras/2c3f7479a496a98d1d7336e20602ed93.webm?t=1769385390\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3569050/extras/2c3f7479a496a98d1d7336e20602ed93.mp4?t=1769385390\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3569050/extras/c72f8bcde62c915c5a30d7ffabdcefcb.poster.avif?t=1769385390\" width=600 height=600 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3569050/extras/c72f8bcde62c915c5a30d7ffabdcefcb.webm?t=1769385390\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3569050/extras/c72f8bcde62c915c5a30d7ffabdcefcb.mp4?t=1769385390\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The more enemies you kill, the more weapons you unlock, and the more enemies that'll spawn (do keep in mind that the bots regularly launch into the air or towards you, and the mechs occasionally fly).</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Don't Die</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >If you die, you lose everything, so make sure to watch your surroundings, otherwise you may get surrounded.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Save Your Progress</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >When you <strong><i>exit to main menu</i></strong>, your progress is saved for next time, but if you die or start a new game, that progress is deleted. </p>",
